metadata.name: Last Hope
metadata.description:
After a global crisis in a dystopian future, low quality of life and high technological development is the sad reality in a chaotic new world.

After several human actions, the sad reality is the reason why for the first time in history that the great nations came together in search of a greater good.


High rates of suicide, depression and anxiety are the biggest pains in this sad scenario. But when there is still one last seed of hope for the good of humanity.

To be continued...
